---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import img2 from '../assets/images/img2.png';
import img3 from '../assets/images/img3.png';
import img4 from '../assets/images/img4.png';
import img5 from '../assets/images/img5.png';
import img6 from '../assets/images/img6.png';
import img7 from '../assets/images/img7.png';
import img8 from '../assets/images/img8.png';
import img9 from '../assets/images/img9.png';
import img10 from '../assets/images/img10.png';
import img11 from '../assets/images/img11.png';
import img12 from '../assets/images/img12.png';
import img13 from '../assets/images/img13.png';
import img14 from '../assets/images/img14.png';
import img15 from '../assets/images/img15.png';
import img16 from '../assets/images/img16.png';
---

<MainLayout title="About Me">
  <article class="space-y-8 md:space-y-10">

    <!-- H1 Sektion -->
    <h1 class="text-center text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-[#53081B] pt-20 sm:pt-24 md:pt-28 pb-6 sm:pb-8 md:pb-10 animate-[bounce_3s_ease-out_2]">
      Who I am and what I do
    </h1>

    <!-- Introduktionstekst -->
    <div class="mx-auto w-[90%] sm:w-[85%] md:w-[50%] bg-[#F0C6B4] p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10">
      <p class="leading-relaxed sm:leading-loose md:leading-loose">
        I am a 23 year old girl located in Vesterbro, Copenhagen. I’m currently in my third semester of Multimedia Design at EK. <br><br>
        Ever since I was young, I’ve loved being creative, and I knew I wanted to pursue a path where I could turn my ideas into real projects, rather than just spending hours studying theory. <br>
        Studying at EK allows me to do just that, and I’m excited to keep developing my skills and bringing my ideas to life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- The Character Sektion -->
    <div class="bg-[rgba(174,51,89,0.6)] py-8 px-4">
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-6" style="font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; color: #53081B">
        The Character
      </h2>

      <div class="flex space-x-4 overflow-x-auto">
        <Image src={img2} alt="image 2" class="flex-shrink-0 w-[200px] h-[250px] sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[375px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[500px] object-cover" />
        <Image src={img3} alt="image 3" class="flex-shrink-0 w-[200px] h-[250px] sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[375px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[500px] object-cover" />
        <Image src={img4} alt="image 4" class="flex-shrink-0 w-[200px] h-[250px] sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[375px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[500px] object-cover" />
        <Image src={img5} alt="image 5" class="flex-shrink-0 w-[200px] h-[250px] sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[375px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[500px] object-cover" />
        <Image src={img6} alt="image 6" class="flex-shrink-0 w-[200px] h-[250px] sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[375px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[500px] object-cover" />
        <Image src={img7} alt="image 7" class="flex-shrink-0 w-[200px] h-[250px] sm:w-[300px] sm:h-[375px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[500px] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Get to know me Sektion -->
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-6" style="font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; color: #AE3359">
      Get to know me
    </h2>

    <div class="mx-auto w-[90%] sm:w-[85%] md:w-[50%] bg-[#F0C6B4] p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10">
      <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl py-4 sm:py-6 md:py-8 text-center">
        Me as a digital designer: <br> my journey, goals, and creative style
      </h3>
      <p class="leading-relaxed sm:leading-loose md:leading-loose">
        My passion is to create! I’ve always been a very creative person, spending hours on different projects to explore and express my creativity. My goal is to turn this passion into my career, working with brands to shape their image, design posts, build branding, and create advertisements that truly stand out. <br><br>
        My creative style is versatile, but I like to keep things simple without ever being boring. I enjoy adding unique elements to bring my work to life—whether it’s playful colors, exciting fonts, eye-catching photos, or other creative details. I believe design should feel both clean and engaging, leaving a lasting impression.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- The Identity Sektion -->
    <div class="bg-[rgba(174,51,89,0.6)] py-8 px-4">
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-6" style="font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; color: #53081B">
        The Identity
      </h2>

      <div class="flex space-x-4 overflow-x-auto">
